text: Shaina Turley (born August 11, 1984) is an American rugby union player. She played for the United States women's national rugby union team at the 2014 Women's Rugby World Cup. She played for University of San Diego. She served in the United States Marine Corps. == References == == Other websites == * Capt Shaina Turley World Rugby, May 8, 2014 Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:American rugby union players
